text.tspan: Practice with one of your organs.
We suggest practicing with your stomach
or heart. Try to feel it, be aware of how
it behaves through out the day. How does
it interact with your other body parts and
They are sticky patches mimicking the size
and texture of a living Symbiorgan.
With a Symbiorgan placeholder, you can
practice the dailylife of having a
Symbiorgan on you, before commit to one.
